(firstQuint)Scalp Cooling to Prevent Chemo-induced Hair Loss.

 Cooling the scalp during chemotherapy may help reduce the chances of losing hair during treatment.

 The investigators are hoping that using the PAXMAN Orbis Scalp Cooling Device may stop patients who are undergoing chemotherapy from losing their hair.

